### Deck of Cards API Tests ###

### Create a new shuffled deck
GET http://localhost:5040/cards/deck/new?deckCount=1

### Create multiple decks (2 decks)
GET http://localhost:5040/cards/deck/new?deckCount=2

### Draw 2 cards from deck (replace DECK_ID with actual deck ID from previous response)
GET http://localhost:5040/cards/deck/DECK_ID/draw?count=2

### Draw 5 cards from deck (replace DECK_ID with actual deck ID)
GET http://localhost:5040/cards/deck/DECK_ID/draw-five

### Shuffle existing deck (replace DECK_ID with actual deck ID)
GET http://localhost:5040/cards/deck/DECK_ID/shuffle

### Complete workflow example ###
# 1. First create a deck, copy the deck_id from response
# 2. Then use that deck_id in the draw cards endpoints below

